description:
The first internet celebrity group, 15 minutes of fame, 4,000 people meet and greets, and standing up to the boss! We have our friend Matthew Espinosa, OG content creator and viral sensation of Vine, Youtube, and Tik Tok. Matt was part of the MAGCON group, originally blown up from Vine, and now XEELA new understudy.


Check out Matt's Podcast called Gen 2 Gen with Erik Griffin here: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/gen2gen/id1581843629
